cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.RO 

This paper is about using deep reinforcement learning to learn to play a 3D game from raw pixels. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also deals with the challenges of learning in complex environments, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.RO (Robotics).
